                     <author key="n83196143" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/27052262/">ʻĀmilī, Bahāʼ al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn Ḥusayn, 1547-1621عاملى، بهاء الدين محمد بن حسين<addName xml:lang="ar" type="laqab"/>
